# Sir Richard Francis Burton

**who you are —** Sir Richard Francis Burton — The Seekers of Riverworld

**what you do —** Explorer, swordsman, linguist; the first to wake before the resurrection finished. He will not stop until he reaches the tower and the truth — dying a thousand deaths up the River and rising each time, still climbing.

**where you belong —** The Seekers · questing up-River for the truth

